WEBVTT

01:40.640 --> 01:45.950
[Speed and Love]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.780
[Episode 24]

01:50.750 --> 01:51.340
Here.

01:51.670 --> 01:53.530
Take a seat. I'll go take a shower.

01:54.140 --> 01:55.870
You're showering in his place?

01:57.590 --> 01:58.420
I stay here.

01:59.030 --> 01:59.470
You...

01:59.550 --> 02:00.700
I can't stand it. I smell terrible.

02:00.700 --> 02:01.490
It's unbearable.

02:01.490 --> 02:03.310
A bunch of men
were smoking around me tonight.

02:03.310 --> 02:04.460
I can't stand the smell of smoke.

02:04.460 --> 02:05.720
Make yourself at home.

02:56.280 --> 02:57.880
You got a phone call just now.

02:59.870 --> 03:00.660
Thank you.

03:02.030 --> 03:03.360
It was from a little boy.

03:04.270 --> 03:05.380
It must be my son.

03:06.000 --> 03:06.910
Son?

03:08.910 --> 03:09.940
Jin Zhao's?

03:10.190 --> 03:10.830
What?

03:11.410 --> 03:13.900
Is Jin Zhao your son's father?

03:14.930 --> 03:15.790
What are you talking about?

03:15.790 --> 03:17.790
My son has already graduated from college.

03:17.790 --> 03:18.660
College?

03:21.750 --> 03:22.500
I'm sorry.

03:22.710 --> 03:25.040
I accidentally saw your phone wallpaper.

03:25.310 --> 03:27.780
A 5 or 6-year-old boy was calling you.

03:29.850 --> 03:31.650
The wallpaper is my younger son.

03:32.020 --> 03:33.480
He's about 5 or 6 years old.

03:34.720 --> 03:35.440
So...

03:36.030 --> 03:37.820
Your younger son's father...

03:38.340 --> 03:39.380
Is he...

03:39.500 --> 03:40.660
Not Jin Zhao.

03:41.550 --> 03:43.480
Young lady, what are you thinking?

03:43.990 --> 03:45.470
Do you know how old I am?

03:48.310 --> 03:49.030
32?

03:51.030 --> 03:52.380
I'm almost 50.

03:52.660 --> 03:53.420
If I tried hard enough,

03:53.420 --> 03:55.420
I could have another child your age.

03:56.000 --> 03:59.060
How could I possibly
have something to do with Jin Zhao?

04:03.150 --> 04:04.810
You look amazing for your age.

04:06.380 --> 04:07.340
I thought...

04:07.750 --> 04:08.670
I thought you...

04:08.670 --> 04:10.330
Thought I was Jin Zhao's wife?

04:18.029 --> 04:19.220
Your name is...

04:19.860 --> 04:20.620
Mu?

04:23.450 --> 04:24.480
No wonder.

04:25.470 --> 04:28.000
You looked familiar
when I saw you at the door.

04:28.030 --> 04:30.290
It just didn't come to mind immediately.

04:31.120 --> 04:31.890
Come with me.

04:38.630 --> 04:41.760
This is Jin Zhao's rehabilitation room.
Please come in.

04:59.100 --> 05:01.100
Is that little girl in the photo you?

05:07.830 --> 05:09.420
Let me properly introduce myself.

05:09.420 --> 05:11.620
I'm Jin Zhao's personal physician, Julia.

05:11.620 --> 05:12.230
Hello.

05:13.430 --> 05:14.160
Personal...

05:14.940 --> 05:15.650
Hello.

05:20.190 --> 05:23.180
During the first two years
after Jin Zhao's accident,

05:23.180 --> 05:24.780
his condition was terrible.

05:24.980 --> 05:27.640
He often experienced pain
throughout his body.

05:28.100 --> 05:29.630
During the worst episodes,

05:30.270 --> 05:31.800
I had to give him sedatives.

05:33.070 --> 05:34.980
When he wasn't fully conscious,

05:36.780 --> 05:38.340
he kept mumbling,

05:38.780 --> 05:39.470
"Mu...

05:41.270 --> 05:41.980
Mu..."

05:43.150 --> 05:44.950
I didn't understand at the time.

05:45.340 --> 05:46.480
I thought it was

05:46.510 --> 05:49.180
the English word "Moon."

05:51.150 --> 05:52.540
Later someone told me

05:53.409 --> 05:54.360
that actually

05:56.550 --> 05:58.140
it was a girl's name:

05:59.030 --> 05:59.860
Jiang Mu.

06:02.590 --> 06:03.790
Your name is Jiang Mu?

06:20.240 --> 06:21.410
What has he

06:23.670 --> 06:25.330
been through all these years?

06:32.470 --> 06:34.000
I was also hired by someone.

06:34.580 --> 06:36.510
Lin Sui brought me back from Canada

06:36.630 --> 06:39.130
to take charge
of Jin Zhao's rehabilitation.

06:39.130 --> 06:41.190
I stayed with him in Chaguo for a year,

06:41.260 --> 06:43.780
which was also when
he was in his worst condition.

06:43.780 --> 06:44.710
You could say

06:46.620 --> 06:48.150
he was on the brink of death.

06:49.390 --> 06:50.150
Later,

06:50.340 --> 06:52.270
when his condition improved a bit,

06:52.510 --> 06:55.110
he insisted on returning
to China, to Nanjing.

06:55.240 --> 06:56.840
Lin Sui and I both disagreed.

06:57.450 --> 06:59.520
Lin Sui talked to him many times.

07:00.300 --> 07:01.830
But he was very determined.

07:02.660 --> 07:03.830
So we discussed it,

07:03.980 --> 07:05.720
and I decided to return to China with him

07:05.720 --> 07:07.040
to live with him

07:07.590 --> 07:08.720
and take care of him.

07:08.980 --> 07:10.640
I'm staying in the guest room.

07:12.060 --> 07:13.180
At that time,

07:13.880 --> 07:15.740
his condition was very unstable.

07:16.290 --> 07:18.130
I was on call day and night.

07:21.950 --> 07:23.600
If he hadn't worn me out,

07:24.390 --> 07:26.190
I'd probably look much younger,

07:26.860 --> 07:27.950
maybe

07:29.070 --> 07:30.300
about 28 years old.

07:34.920 --> 07:36.690
[Jin Zhao]

07:40.780 --> 07:41.580
It's Jin Zhao.

07:49.420 --> 07:50.180
Jin Zhao.

07:52.470 --> 07:54.300
I've brought back
all the medicine you need,

07:54.300 --> 07:56.360
and wrote down all the instructions.

07:58.510 --> 08:00.110
I'm not going back to Canada.

08:02.530 --> 08:03.360
Of course,

08:04.070 --> 08:05.800
if you don't need me around

08:05.830 --> 08:07.240
and have someone else to keep you company,

08:07.240 --> 08:09.450
I wouldn't mind taking some time off.

08:10.030 --> 08:10.950
My eldest

08:11.100 --> 08:12.470
has been asking me
to go to his graduation ceremony for ages.

08:12.470 --> 08:13.740
I want to go.

08:16.270 --> 08:17.340
I don't believe you can

08:17.340 --> 08:18.910
take care of yourself.

08:22.830 --> 08:23.510
Fine.

08:24.350 --> 08:26.350
Without this old witch—me—around,

08:28.180 --> 08:29.860
go find your little angel.

08:33.400 --> 08:34.760
Fine. Bye.

08:42.750 --> 08:43.820
Jin Zhao has had

08:44.510 --> 08:46.440
a very difficult time these years.

08:47.030 --> 08:48.760
It's really good that you can be

08:49.190 --> 08:50.450
back by his side again.

09:07.230 --> 09:08.940
Jin Zhao is truly strong.

09:09.590 --> 09:11.990
He has extraordinary willpower.

09:12.750 --> 09:14.210
You must not give up on him.

09:24.310 --> 09:29.100
[Purple Mountain Observatory]

09:31.030 --> 09:31.660
Nana.

09:32.460 --> 09:33.660
This is from Director Wang.

09:33.660 --> 09:34.490
It's for Monday's meeting.

09:34.490 --> 09:35.370
Okay.

09:36.270 --> 09:36.870
Mu.

09:37.180 --> 09:38.410
This is our schedule.

09:38.700 --> 09:40.230
On Monday, we need to confirm

09:40.230 --> 09:41.270
the venue setup.

09:41.390 --> 09:43.000
You might need to double-check everything.

09:43.000 --> 09:43.450
Okay.

09:43.470 --> 09:44.400
That's about it.

10:06.100 --> 10:06.830
You...

10:27.570 --> 10:28.750
Hello, to Manshi please.

10:28.750 --> 10:30.480
Alright, please wait a moment.

10:33.700 --> 10:35.630
Do you have any luggage to check in?

10:37.640 --> 10:38.610
The boarding gate is this way.

10:38.610 --> 10:40.270
-Have a good trip.
-Thank you.

10:54.700 --> 10:56.030
You're Jiang Mu, right?

10:56.460 --> 10:57.290
Dr. Julia asked me

10:57.290 --> 10:59.120
to give you this medical file.

10:59.560 --> 11:00.250
Thank you.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.150
Jiang Mu.

11:53.700 --> 11:55.670
I know you're in Chaguo now.

11:59.760 --> 12:01.400
Why wasn't I told anything?

12:02.820 --> 12:05.180
Since you know everything now,

12:05.660 --> 12:08.110
what do you plan to do?

12:24.710 --> 12:26.080
[Patient Medical Report]

12:39.180 --> 12:40.180
Is there any news

12:40.700 --> 12:41.700
from Jin Zhao?

12:44.420 --> 12:46.220
He hasn't been back physically.

12:46.500 --> 12:48.300
We haven't heard much from him
in a long time.

12:48.300 --> 12:50.960
Yeah,
it's been so many years since he returned.

12:51.150 --> 12:52.060
Who knows,

12:52.470 --> 12:54.750
maybe he's already
settled down somewhere else.

12:54.750 --> 12:56.610
I might have some bad news for you.

12:58.110 --> 12:58.780
What is it?

13:00.330 --> 13:01.590
Lightning is missing.

13:02.870 --> 13:03.580
Missing?

13:03.780 --> 13:05.580
Then I got a call from a stranger.

13:05.630 --> 13:06.750
He said he had the goods

13:06.750 --> 13:08.580
and quoted me a price.

13:08.870 --> 13:09.990
I thought it was a scam,

13:09.990 --> 13:11.920
so I insisted on meeting in person.

13:12.060 --> 13:13.030
To my surprise,

13:13.270 --> 13:14.420
it was Brandy!

13:14.790 --> 13:15.920
You're still young.

13:18.460 --> 13:20.660
We'll have plenty of time in the future.

13:21.970 --> 13:23.330
But your mom can't wait.

13:24.300 --> 13:26.110
After major surgery,

13:27.030 --> 13:29.300
a patient's mood is
the most important thing.

13:29.300 --> 13:30.660
If you stay with her,

13:30.940 --> 13:32.270
she will feel better.

13:33.150 --> 13:34.680
It's good for her recovery.

13:49.190 --> 13:51.060
[Jin Zhao]

13:57.800 --> 13:58.560
Are you busy?

14:00.480 --> 14:01.170
I'm at home.

14:02.350 --> 14:03.810
Do you have time to meet up?

14:04.870 --> 14:06.270
I have something for you.

14:08.910 --> 14:09.720
No.

14:13.250 --> 14:14.850
Then when will you have time?

14:17.780 --> 14:19.780
Come for a walk with me this weekend.

14:24.540 --> 14:26.200
Forget it if you don't want to.

14:26.460 --> 14:27.460
Anyway, back then

14:28.030 --> 14:30.290
you promised to take me out but never did.

14:30.370 --> 14:31.630
I still remember that.

14:37.700 --> 14:39.960
Will going for a walk
make you less angry?

14:40.170 --> 14:40.890
No.

14:44.910 --> 14:46.170
So are you still going?

14:50.590 --> 14:51.160
Yes.

14:52.180 --> 14:53.980
Let's go for a walk this weekend.

15:36.570 --> 15:38.370
Why are you just standing there?

15:41.500 --> 15:43.980
I'm looking at how
you haven't changed at all.

15:43.980 --> 15:44.770
What about me?

15:44.440 --> 15:47.800
♪ What was it that brought me to you? ♪

15:45.030 --> 15:46.160
Have I changed a lot?

15:48.200 --> 15:50.110
♪ Perhaps it was fate's design ♪

15:50.670 --> 15:54.410
♪ Through all our winding paths,
we always find each other ♪

15:54.180 --> 15:54.910
Quite a lot.

15:54.430 --> 15:58.030
♪ The storm turned to rain,
and everything was swept away ♪

15:57.270 --> 15:59.230
Was I prettier before or now?

15:58.060 --> 15:59.770
♪ Slowly, everything becomes clear ♪

15:59.790 --> 16:02.150
♪ In your gaze ♪

16:00.990 --> 16:02.580
I only want a three-word answer.

16:02.440 --> 16:04.400
♪ I found the answer ♪

16:04.430 --> 16:06.470
♪ There's a feeling so strong ♪

16:05.030 --> 16:06.490
You're always beautiful.

16:06.500 --> 16:09.630
♪ Our story is still unfolding ♪

16:09.770 --> 16:13.680
♪ Waiting for the perfect ending ♪

16:15.390 --> 16:17.840
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

16:17.860 --> 16:20.330
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

16:20.360 --> 16:23.480
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

16:21.150 --> 16:22.060
Brother,

16:22.300 --> 16:24.750
when will we get there? I'm so tired.

16:23.500 --> 16:25.310
♪ I just can't help it ♪

16:25.330 --> 16:27.780
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

16:25.910 --> 16:26.700
We're almost there.

16:26.700 --> 16:27.940
Just a few more steps
and we'll see the sunset.

16:27.810 --> 16:30.310
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

16:28.110 --> 16:30.630
But Brother, I really can't walk anymore.

16:30.330 --> 16:33.340
♪ Sweet longing drifts on the wind ♪

16:30.910 --> 16:31.970
I'm stopping here.

16:32.150 --> 16:33.360
I'll just sit right here.

16:33.360 --> 16:35.580
♪ I can feel you near ♪

16:34.350 --> 16:34.990
Come on.

16:35.610 --> 16:38.040
♪ Feel you're with me ♪

16:35.750 --> 16:37.010
Don't worry, I'm here.

16:37.230 --> 16:38.230
I'll help you walk up.

16:38.060 --> 16:40.360
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

16:40.540 --> 16:42.600
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

16:42.950 --> 16:44.630
♪ You're the only one in my heart ♪

16:44.650 --> 16:47.320
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

16:47.350 --> 16:49.480
♪ The road ahead ♪

16:49.740 --> 16:51.740
♪ And every step we take ♪

16:51.760 --> 16:54.380
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

16:51.940 --> 16:52.630
Here we are.

16:54.810 --> 16:57.660
♪ Just to see you ♪

17:06.450 --> 17:07.119
Here you go.

17:11.109 --> 17:12.420
Why are you giving me a phone?

17:12.420 --> 17:15.480
Didn't you say you wanted to replace
your phone after using it for years?

17:15.480 --> 17:16.810
Since you're often out,

17:16.810 --> 17:18.670
you should use something better.

17:25.109 --> 17:26.020
Is that funny?

17:26.500 --> 17:28.550
Will you believe anything I say?

17:28.870 --> 17:29.800
Being like this,

17:29.980 --> 17:32.460
you'll easily get scammed by other girls.

17:34.330 --> 17:35.790
You're not "other girls."

17:36.560 --> 17:37.520
Then what am I?

17:50.980 --> 17:51.630
Um,

17:51.870 --> 17:54.350
before we start,
I need to confirm something.

17:54.350 --> 17:55.950
You're still single, right?

17:57.850 --> 17:59.390
What does being single
have to do with this?

17:59.390 --> 18:00.460
Of course it does.

18:00.910 --> 18:02.570
I'm a person with principles.

18:02.690 --> 18:04.740
I would never interfere
in someone else's relationship.

18:04.740 --> 18:05.830
So I must confirm.

18:12.020 --> 18:14.150
I thought we were just going for a walk?

18:14.350 --> 18:15.070
What?

18:15.850 --> 18:17.850
What are you planning to do to me here

18:18.190 --> 18:20.790
that involves
interfering in relationships?

18:27.910 --> 18:29.980
You don't seem to have any concerns.

18:30.390 --> 18:31.740
Aren't you worried that
my boyfriend might mind

18:31.740 --> 18:33.200
that you got me a new phone?

18:33.340 --> 18:35.120
If he minds, can't he buy one himself?

18:35.120 --> 18:36.120
His money

18:36.460 --> 18:38.980
is for buying gaming equipment.

18:50.180 --> 18:51.980
Why did you walk off by yourself?

18:53.310 --> 18:55.510
Have you climbed this mountain before?

18:56.740 --> 18:57.500
No.

18:59.180 --> 19:01.200
Isn't the coffee shop very close to here?

19:01.200 --> 19:02.860
Why didn't you come climbing?

19:04.600 --> 19:05.530
No reason.

19:50.030 --> 19:52.230
When did you start liking photography?

19:59.720 --> 20:01.320
What are you photographing?

20:02.900 --> 20:03.760
Try feeling it.

20:09.720 --> 20:10.920
I don't quite feel it.

20:13.040 --> 20:14.500
Capturing nature's soul.

20:17.830 --> 20:19.420
How did I never notice before

20:19.420 --> 20:21.680
that you're so good at talking nonsense?

20:38.050 --> 20:39.780
I noticed it at the coffee shop.

20:48.830 --> 20:50.290
Why do you keep wearing it?

21:04.610 --> 21:05.500
Let's compete.

21:05.700 --> 21:07.030
Let's see who's faster.

21:07.980 --> 21:08.610
No.

21:09.020 --> 21:09.830
Why not?

21:14.420 --> 21:15.220
You go first.

21:15.740 --> 21:17.000
I'll catch up with you.

21:20.310 --> 21:21.770
I'll wait for you up there.

22:19.720 --> 22:20.780
This is far enough.

22:21.310 --> 22:23.240
He should be able to keep up, right?

22:25.420 --> 22:26.180
Zhao.

22:27.070 --> 22:28.560
Why don't you tell me

22:28.590 --> 22:30.250
about your health condition?

22:58.900 --> 22:59.620
Jin Zhao!

23:08.660 --> 23:10.320
Are you going to hide forever?

23:33.740 --> 23:34.550
Jin Zhao!

23:37.480 --> 23:39.140
Are you going to hide forever?

23:47.590 --> 23:49.190
That day I went to your place,

23:50.330 --> 23:52.660
Dr. Julia told me everything.

23:57.660 --> 23:59.090
I also went to Manshi.

24:02.020 --> 24:04.550
I saw all your medical reports.

24:09.090 --> 24:10.620
Why didn't you tell me?

24:21.180 --> 24:22.990
If I hadn't gone to your house,

24:25.820 --> 24:28.080
how long were you going to hide it from me?

24:29.440 --> 24:31.200
For the rest of your life?

24:31.880 --> 24:36.800
♪ Forgotten between the rearview mirror ♪

24:38.990 --> 24:44.370
♪ Seeing your long unseen face
on that rainy night ♪

24:39.290 --> 24:40.160
I'm sorry.

24:43.550 --> 24:44.700
I was thinking

24:46.700 --> 24:52.180
♪ Counting backwards to
the unfulfilled promises ♪

24:47.260 --> 24:48.700
I would go look for you

24:49.940 --> 24:51.540
when my condition improved.

24:53.710 --> 24:59.370
♪ The heart that is still beating
hasn't said goodbye yet ♪

24:56.630 --> 24:57.750
Why?

25:00.300 --> 25:03.150
♪ Meeting again after many years ♪

25:01.700 --> 25:04.940
Why did all of you keep this from me?

25:03.640 --> 25:06.550
♪ The coffee is too sour and bitter;
I'm greedy for something sweet ♪

25:06.350 --> 25:08.260
Why didn't you tell me?

25:07.690 --> 25:10.320
♪ Who will circle around the line
bordering the thoughts? ♪

25:09.870 --> 25:10.940
No matter what，

25:10.680 --> 25:14.810
♪ Stupidly,
I refuse to believe there's an end ♪

25:11.220 --> 25:13.460
you should have at least let me know.

25:15.580 --> 25:17.570
♪ I must ♪

25:17.590 --> 25:21.410
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

25:21.430 --> 25:24.840
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

25:25.050 --> 25:26.570
♪ Willingly ♪

25:29.190 --> 25:32.410
♪ At this moment ♪

25:29.700 --> 25:31.160
You were still young then.

25:32.460 --> 25:33.500
I couldn't bear to.

25:32.630 --> 25:36.070
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

25:34.310 --> 25:36.700
But you could bear
not contacting me at all?

25:36.090 --> 25:40.610
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

25:40.650 --> 25:43.820
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

25:42.910 --> 25:43.700
Jin Zhao...

25:48.870 --> 25:50.460
You're so heartless.

26:02.340 --> 26:08.060
♪ I really want to fill
the void of regret ♪

26:09.300 --> 26:11.820
♪ My longing has left the bow ♪

26:11.840 --> 26:15.740
♪ Shooting out into the horizon ♪

26:16.080 --> 26:18.990
♪ Meeting again after many years ♪

26:19.460 --> 26:22.230
♪ The coffee is too sour;
I'm greedy for something sweet ♪

26:23.500 --> 26:24.420
At first,

26:23.660 --> 26:26.290
♪ Who will circle around the line
bordering the thoughts? ♪

26:26.650 --> 26:30.780
♪ Stupidly,
I refuse to believe there's an end ♪

26:28.630 --> 26:30.090
my condition wasn't good.

26:31.550 --> 26:33.540
♪ I must ♪

26:32.890 --> 26:34.930
I didn't know if I could make it.

26:33.560 --> 26:37.380
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

26:36.790 --> 26:38.310
So I made Sanlai promise me

26:37.400 --> 26:40.810
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

26:38.420 --> 26:39.820
not to tell you the truth.

26:41.020 --> 26:42.540
♪ Willingly ♪

26:42.020 --> 26:43.350
Later I pulled through,

26:45.150 --> 26:47.150
but I didn't even have a place to stay.

26:45.160 --> 26:48.380
♪ At this moment ♪

26:48.590 --> 26:49.700
In that situation,

26:48.600 --> 26:52.040
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

26:51.390 --> 26:52.630
I couldn't contact you.

26:52.060 --> 26:56.580
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

26:52.940 --> 26:53.590
Then why

26:53.590 --> 26:56.050
did you suddenly appear
in my life again now?

26:56.620 --> 26:59.790
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

27:01.740 --> 27:03.940
♪ Look at the days that have passed ♪

27:04.130 --> 27:07.890
♪ Those were yesterday's youth ♪

27:08.690 --> 27:12.080
♪ Look at the people
parting in the crowd ♪

27:12.380 --> 27:15.990
♪ They used to love each other the most ♪

27:16.020 --> 27:18.650
♪ Look at what the vast world wants ♪

27:18.890 --> 27:19.610
Are you...

27:18.960 --> 27:23.040
♪ It's nothing but a fairytale ♪

27:21.310 --> 27:23.310
Are you trying to reconcile with me?

27:23.400 --> 27:26.790
♪ It's always the broken up couple ♪

27:27.170 --> 27:30.040
♪ Who reunite amidst love, hate,
and separation ♪

27:30.320 --> 27:32.290
♪ I must ♪

27:32.700 --> 27:36.520
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

27:36.540 --> 27:39.950
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

27:40.160 --> 27:41.680
♪ Willingly ♪

27:44.300 --> 27:47.520
♪ At this moment ♪

27:47.740 --> 27:51.180
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

27:51.200 --> 27:52.690
♪ Don't ask about the past ♪

27:52.720 --> 27:55.730
♪ Just bet on tomorrow ♪

27:55.750 --> 27:58.810
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

27:58.840 --> 28:03.110
♪ The trails overlap again ♪

28:24.660 --> 28:25.420
Later,

28:25.580 --> 28:27.780
when his condition improved slightly,

28:27.790 --> 28:30.390
he insisted on returning
to China, to Nanjing.

28:30.550 --> 28:32.150
Lin Sui and I both disagreed.

28:32.260 --> 28:33.260
Lin Sui spent a long time

28:33.260 --> 28:34.790
trying to talk him out of it.

28:35.330 --> 28:37.050
But he was very determined.

28:38.860 --> 28:41.120
Why did he insist on coming back to China?

28:41.590 --> 28:43.180
Why did he buy the old house?

28:56.810 --> 28:59.670
You want to meet Jiang Mu?
Are you crazy or am I crazy?

29:01.080 --> 29:02.230
Her mom is sick.

29:02.590 --> 29:03.990
She needs to go to Canada.

29:04.680 --> 29:06.640
I must let her know I'm okay

29:07.190 --> 29:09.520
so she can stay in Canada
with peace of mind

29:09.790 --> 29:12.520
and accompany her mother
for medical treatment.

29:15.110 --> 29:15.830
Brandy,

29:17.550 --> 29:19.550
tell me how you're going to meet her.

29:20.020 --> 29:20.650
Like this?

29:21.110 --> 29:21.710
Like this?

29:22.110 --> 29:22.940
How?

29:23.940 --> 29:24.630
Look at your condition.

29:24.630 --> 29:26.360
You'll scare Jiang Mu to death.

29:29.200 --> 29:31.600
Besides, the doctors would never allow it.

29:31.660 --> 29:33.390
Don't worry about the doctors.

29:33.560 --> 29:35.420
Officer Lu will help us with that.

29:36.350 --> 29:37.790
What I need you to do now

29:38.150 --> 29:39.680
is take me to the coffee shop

29:40.260 --> 29:41.520
and then bring Mu over.

29:45.760 --> 29:46.430
Brandy,

29:46.980 --> 29:48.440
let's think this through.

29:49.920 --> 29:51.960
You barely survived.

29:53.260 --> 29:55.260
What if something goes wrong again?

29:57.350 --> 29:58.030
Sanlai,

30:00.420 --> 30:01.550
I've made up my mind.

30:57.500 --> 30:58.180
Brandy!

30:59.190 --> 31:00.460
Are you okay? Get up.

31:01.600 --> 31:02.200
Come on.

31:12.230 --> 31:12.830
Let's go.

31:13.220 --> 31:14.880
I'll take you to the hospital.

31:17.180 --> 31:19.180
Looking at her tear-reddened eyes,

31:20.180 --> 31:21.780
I wanted so badly to hold her,

31:22.650 --> 31:23.700
but I couldn't.

31:25.110 --> 31:26.570
I only want her to be happy,

31:27.810 --> 31:29.200
even if that happiness

31:30.700 --> 31:31.830
doesn't include me.

31:48.660 --> 31:52.930
[Jin Zhao]

32:04.420 --> 32:06.440
Jin Zhao's rehabilitation
is very tough.

32:06.440 --> 32:07.840
You need to encourage him more.

32:07.840 --> 32:09.700
Observe his physical reactions.

32:10.020 --> 32:10.850
Pay attention to Jin Zhao's

32:10.850 --> 32:13.350
complexion and breathing
for any abnormalities.

32:13.350 --> 32:15.350
If dizziness or severe pain occurs,

32:15.410 --> 32:17.270
stop immediately and contact me.

32:46.560 --> 32:49.100
[Purple Mountain Observatory]

32:52.020 --> 32:53.390
Mu, I'm leaving now.

32:53.740 --> 32:54.740
See you tomorrow.

32:55.460 --> 32:56.020
Nana.

32:56.600 --> 32:58.500
It's Mid-Autumn Festival today.
Let's have dinner together.

32:58.500 --> 32:59.110
Sure.

33:05.010 --> 33:05.600
Let's go.

33:38.420 --> 33:40.350
Today is the Mid-Autumn Festival.

33:40.500 --> 33:41.960
My family is all in Canada.

33:42.110 --> 33:43.440
I'm celebrating alone.

33:44.920 --> 33:45.880
I'm sorry,

33:46.660 --> 33:47.720
I can't be with you.

33:54.510 --> 33:56.570
I have something to do during the day.

34:07.500 --> 34:09.159
Is the coffee shop open today?

34:12.540 --> 34:14.070
It's opened till 4 o'clock.

35:16.670 --> 35:17.400
Are you home?

35:21.820 --> 35:23.270
I think I forgot to add vinegar.

35:23.270 --> 35:24.910
It's fine. Having food is good enough.

35:24.910 --> 35:26.140
It smells delicious. Try it quickly.

35:26.140 --> 35:26.710
Really?

35:26.730 --> 35:27.660
Look at this roe.

35:28.980 --> 35:29.750
Not bad at all.

35:29.750 --> 35:30.390
Right?

35:32.380 --> 35:33.500
You came just in time.

35:33.500 --> 35:34.460
Want some crab?

35:39.670 --> 35:40.250
No, thanks.

35:40.250 --> 35:41.910
I brought you some mooncakes.

35:44.270 --> 35:45.910
Where did all these crabs come from?

35:45.910 --> 35:47.940
They were all gifts
from clients to Boss.

35:47.940 --> 35:49.750
But Boss has a cold and fever recently,

35:49.750 --> 35:50.980
so can't eat cold-natured food.

35:50.980 --> 35:52.710
That's why we get to enjoy them.

35:53.230 --> 35:54.420
Your boss is sick?

35:55.310 --> 35:57.060
Seems he caught a cold over the weekend

35:57.060 --> 35:58.420
and got sick.

36:06.060 --> 36:07.190
Out to greet guests?

36:17.590 --> 36:18.850
Are you going to pay me?

36:23.010 --> 36:24.070
I can't afford you.

36:25.460 --> 36:27.420
I haven't even named my price.

36:37.980 --> 36:38.710
Boss.

36:39.270 --> 36:40.420
Finished with your IV drip?

36:40.420 --> 36:41.580
So quick today?

36:42.430 --> 36:43.120
It's fine.

36:43.640 --> 36:44.600
Well...

36:45.230 --> 36:47.310
You should go home early for the holiday.

36:47.310 --> 36:49.310
-Thank you, Boss.
-Thank you, Boss.

36:50.000 --> 36:52.330
He said he had something to do
during the day.

36:52.330 --> 36:55.260
So that "something"
was actually getting an IV drip.

36:55.640 --> 36:57.970
Going to the hospital alone on a festival.

36:58.280 --> 37:00.480
I would have gone with him if I had known.

37:04.750 --> 37:05.950
Still having a fever?

37:59.610 --> 38:00.440
Feel for yourself.
